  "texts": [
    "Machine learning models can analyze chemical profiles and sensory data to identify ingredient combinations that enhance taste and texture.",
    "These models help reduce off-notes and improve mouthfeel, making plantbased alternatives more appealing.",
    "AI also supports the repurposing of food byproducts and underutilized crops by predicting their sensory and functional properties, which promotes waste reduction and supports circular food systems.",
    "Together, these applications demonstrate how AI can advance both sensory quality and sustainability in food innovation.",
    "Beyond the themes of personalization and sustainability, advancements in technology may also catalyze the emergence of new market models."
  ],
